{"content": "I need to multiply 324 \u00d7 523 in base 9.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n- 324\u2089 = 3\u00d79\u00b2 + 2\u00d79\u00b9 + 4\u00d79\u2070 = 3\u00d781 + 2\u00d79 + 4\u00d71 = 243 + 18 + 4 = 265\u2081\u2080\n- 523\u2089 = 5\u00d79\u00b2 + 2\u00d79\u00b9 + 3\u00d79\u2070 = 5\u00d781 + 2\u00d79 + 3\u00d71 = 405 + 18 + 3 = 426\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n- 265 \u00d7 426 = 112,890\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n- 112890 \u00f7 9 = 12543 r 3\n- 12543 \u00f7 9 = 1393 r 6\n- 1393 \u00f7 9 = 154 r 7\n- 154 \u00f7 9 = 17 r 1\n- 17 \u00f7 9 = 1 r 8\n- 1 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 1\n\nReading from bottom to top: **181763\u2089**\n\n181763", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 827, "completion_tokens": 344}